entries.notit_1: This isn't the information I was expecting. Don't you have a datadisk for me?
entries.npc_smuggle_1: Thanks for meeting me. Here are some important findings from the Ministry of Science in Theed. I'm getting back to town before something else jumps me.
entries.npc_breech_1: It's about time you got here.
entries.dontknowyou_1: If you're looking for someone, I'm pretty sure it isn't me.
entries.otherescort_1: I'm sorry, I'm here to meet someone else.
entries.npc_failure_1: How disappointing. I was sure you'd be able to handle this.
entries.npc_noloc_1: I seem to have lost his location coordinates. Come back and see me in a few minutes -- I'll have found them by then.
entries.npc_work_1: Have you picked up that message yet? Shouldn't you be going then?
entries.npc_reward_1: Thanks. Let's see here -- well! Something called the Berserker Virus is making the wildlife more aggressive. I guess maybe you figured that already.
entries.npc_backtowork_1: Were you going to meet that courier, or did something else come up?
entries.npc_4_1: Dee'ja Peak is a beautiful place to study nature. That's how I wound up here. I arrived to study wildlife and never left. I think they just gave me this groundskeeper job so I wouldn't look like a transient. What do you think, can you pick up the disc?
entries.npc_3_1: Oh well, I'll try to find someone else. Thanks anyway.
entries.npc_2_1: Good, you can help me by meeting Bor Ting and bringing his message back here. Keep aware -- it wouldn't do for both of you to get hurt.
entries.npc_1_1: Hi! Are you looking for work? I have a little errand I could use help with. A courier is supposed to bring me a datadisk, but he's having some trouble getting here. He took a minor leg injury when some creature surprised him. Nothing too serious, I assume. Could you bring me the disk?
entries.notyet: I'm too busy to talk to just anyone right now.
entries.npc_reset_1: I'm sorry to hear that. If you feel like you're more capable of doing the job later, I'd be happy to work with you in the future.
entries.cantwork: I'm sure I can find some work for you when you've finished your current assignment.
entries.next: You've been a great help. I'll keep you in mind for future work.
